OL,3,CWalsall woman left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after unnecessary botched
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FWalsall Healthcare NHS Trust has
OL,8,Fapologised after surgeon Mian Munawar
OL,9,FShah botched operations so badly, that
OL,10,Fsome had the wrong bones removed and
OL,11,Fwere left in agonising pain for years.
OL,13,FA total of 91 patients were found
OL,14,Fsuffering with moderate or severe
OL,15,Fharm. Among them, is Angela Glover who
OL,16,Freceived unnecessary treatment.
