OL,7,FAngela worked at Walsall Manor
OL,8,FHospital, and had a muscle tear after
OL,9,Fhelping a patient at the hospital. She
OL,10,Fdidn't question the integrity of the
OL,11,Fhospital or the doctors, and believed
OL,12,Fit when Mr Shah said she had a partial
OL,13,Fshoulder dislocation.
OL,15,FShe made the decision to have surgery,
OL,16,Fbut she said "the next day I was back
OL,17,Fin A&E straight away in excruciating
OL,18,Fpain.
