OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,F"I was in and out of clinics, things
OL,8,Fweren't improving. I had a mental
OL,9,Fhealth breakdown. I basically went
OL,10,Fmissing.
OL,12,F"Nobody was listening, I kept telling
OL,13,Feverybody something was wrong and no-
OL,14,Fone was listening".
OL,16,FShe had a CT scan where it was made
OL,17,Fobvious something wasn't right. She
OL,18,Fhas had five or six follow up
OL,19,Fsurgeries in total since, but has been
OL,20,Fleft in pain for over seven years.
