OL,3,CWalsall woman left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after unnecessary botched
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,F"I know now that I didn't need
OL,8,Fanything and then I got surgery that I
OL,9,Fdidn't need it was an unnecessary
OL,10,Fshoulder operation. It's left me with
OL,11,Fa disability for life. It's life-
OL,12,Fchanging.
OL,14,F"I can't do the things that I used to
OL,15,Fdo". "I just had a new grand-daughter
OL,16,Fand I can't physically pick her up due
OL,17,Fto the pain.
OL,19,F"I don't feel like there's any
OL,20,Fjustice".
