OL,4,Cinjuries after unnecessary botched
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,F"I'm upset, I'm still very angry. I'm
OL,8,Fhaving to have CBD and trauma therapy
OL,9,Fto deal with this anger.
OL,11,F"I live on medication". "I'm in pain
OL,12,Fevery day.
OL,14,F"He should be in a courtroom for what
OL,15,Fhe's done. It's not just me there's
OL,16,Fothers in Walsall. How can you just
OL,17,Fwalk into the sunset?"
OL,19,F"It's over for them, but it's not over
OL,20,Ffor us".
