OL,12,FIn response, Joanne Chadwick-Bell,
OL,13,FChief Executive for Walsall NHS Trust,
OL,14,Fsaid: "I want to unreservedly
OL,15,Fapologise for the 91 patients who have
OL,16,Fundergone treatment with us, where we
OL,17,Fhaven't given them the outcomes we
OL,18,Fexpect.
