OL,7,F"I also want to recognise that those
OL,8,Fpatients who didn't get the care they
OL,9,Fdeserved.
OL,11,F"It would have been distressing them
OL,12,Fto have to relive some of those
OL,13,Fexperiences.
OL,15,FWhen asked if there was a danger that
OL,16,Fanother surgeon could operate within
OL,17,Fthe trust again, she said: "We've put
OL,18,Fa number of things in place from a
OL,19,Fgovernance perspective to make sure
OL,20,Fthis doesn't happen again".
